snippet.title: Rain on Your Parade - Available Now!
snippet.description: Travel the world as a cute cardboard cloud and ruin everybody's day! Unlock new methods of mischief in over 50 levels, each with unique setting and objectives. Make new friends and help them too - it's an adorable schadenfreude game!
